{
 "name": "RPlog_Muera_la_revolucion",
 "title": "Muera la Revolucion",
 "summary": "In the library of his untouched Corellian estate, Kartathia Manor, Lord Geophreigh Smitherbodkins receives a Zabrak visitor, the laconic pilot-for-hire Meissa, to discuss a delicate job. Over a drink served by his Kubaz butler J'Eeves, Smitherbodkins probes whether the 'pilot' might also serve as a bounty hunter, and Meissa coolly negotiates his price before the target is named: G. S. Qwynt VIII, former Prex of the Direx Board, who has stolen a CSA Star Destroyer and styled himself leader of a rebel movement. Recognizing he could have charged far more for such a fortress of a target, Meissa accepts the contract, sealing the dangerous bargain with a handshake.",
